# Working dropboxes — raw uploads before they get processed/placed
/Extra/
/static/models/wildlife/incoming/

# Local cold-storage for assets we've replaced/removed. Kept on disk for
# fast reference but never committed — git history holds the originals if
# they're ever needed back.
/_archive/

# Verification sandbox — playwright harness scripts (verify-*.mjs) AND the
# screenshots they produce. Everything in this folder stays local; future
# Claude sessions read it to see what's already been driven and write new
# probes/shots into it. NEVER commit anything from here.
/.verify/

# Ad-hoc perf probe — playwright-driven scene measurement, regenerated
# as needed during optimization passes.
/perf-probe.mjs

# Raw audio sources before MP3 conversion. Kept locally so the conversion
# can be re-run if MP3s need to be regenerated; never shipped.
/.audio-originals/

# Brainstorm-skill visual companion — persisted mockups + state.
/.superpowers/
# --- Dev-only working files — kept on disk for reference, never published ---
# These are how the world was BUILT (Blender pipeline, research, planning,
# design logs). They add nothing for someone visiting the live site or
# browsing the public repo, so they're untracked. Originals also live in git
# history if ever needed back. To resume a build, the files are right here on
# disk; just point Claude at the path.

# Blender world-build pipeline: Python scripts, .blend files, compression
# utilities, extraction scripts, approval mockups. (~46 MB)
/tools/

# Research, specs, plans, handoffs and runtime-phase planning docs.
# NOTE: docs/day.webp + docs/night.webp ARE committed (README banner).
docs/superpowers/
docs/v3-runtime/
docs/bruno-devlogs/

# World-design decision logs + bulk Bruno extraction artifacts.
/reports/

# Agent context file (CLAUDE.md is kept public; AGENTS.md is dev-only).
AGENTS.md

# Stray shadow-verification probe.
/.verify-shadows.mjs

.superpowers/
